image_analysis.description: An interior photograph of a staircase. The stairs are covered in a grey, patterned carpet. A blue-painted metal railing with a wooden handrail runs along the left side. The walls are painted an off-white or light beige color. On the landing wall, there is a framed picture of a coastal scene and a circular, glowing wall-mounted light fixture above it. An electrical outlet is visible on the wall near the stairs.
